high_descs: Pick up the apple from the table.
Bring the apple to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Bring the apple to the table.
Put the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn around.  Move across the room to the end of the white table.
Pick up the green apple that is closest to the end corner of the table.
Turn around.  Move across the room to the fridge. Open the door.
Place the apple on the shelf to cool.  Close the door.  Open the door.  Pick up the apple off the shelf.
Close the door and turn around.  Move across the room to the white table.
Place the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Cooling an apple in the fridge & returning it to the table.

high_descs: Turn right and move toward the door, then turn right and move to the corner of the room next to the garbage bag, then turn right and face the table next to the window.
Pick up the apple on the front corner of the table that is to the right of the knife.
Turn right and move to the refrigerator in the corner of the room next to the garbage bin.
Open the refrigerator, place the apple on the shelf above the drawer, chill the apple, open the refrigerator, pick up the apple, and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn around and move to the garbage bag in the corner of the room then turn right and face the table.
Place the apple on the edge of the table to the right of the knife and in front of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple on the table.
